NY City Bike Share

Lenka Rozborilova

18/01/2021

The following report presents an insight into the New York City’s bike share system - one of the largest bike shares in the US. The descriptive analysis was carried out on an available data set of 10 bikes that were monitored during the year of 2018.

Here’s a graph of an average usage of a NYC City’s bike throughout the year of 2018

This graph represents the total duration of City Bike hire of the observed 10 bikes in 2018
